title: Boost your power. Get vaccinated. Vaccination Week in the Americas 2015
description: The 13th Vaccination Week in the Americas (VWA) will be celebrated from April 25th to May 2nd, 2015. The regional slogan for VWA 2015 is “Boost your power! Get vaccinated!” www.paho.org/vwa/
